Ted, not at their waists.

44
00:02:13,625 --> 00:02:15,304
Hello, sweetheart.

45
00:02:15,339 --> 00:02:16,449
Hello.

46
00:02:16,484 --> 00:02:18,490
We're having a child-care problem.

47
00:02:18,525 --> 00:02:20,582
Oh. Have you checked out Veridian daycare?

48
00:02:20,617 --> 00:02:24,394
Apparently, several of the janitorial staff
came up through there. They rave about it.

49
00:02:24,468 --> 00:02:27,395
Uh, yeah, I’m just a little
overprotective, you know,

50
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,499
since, uh...

51
00:02:30,285 --> 00:02:31,739
her mom left.

52
00:02:31,774 --> 00:02:33,849
Oh. Sad.

53
00:02:34,490 --> 00:02:37,365
Well, you're always welcome
here, daughter of Ted.

54
00:02:37,483 --> 00:02:39,101
- Rose.
- I know her name.

55
00:02:39,136 --> 00:02:41,444
- Rose's name.
- You know, sweetheart, sometimes, your father--

56
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:43,729
- Ted!
- I know everyone's name.

57
00:02:47,144 --> 00:02:49,571
Once we determined the
type of delivery system,

58
00:02:49,606 --> 00:02:53,576
